headline: GE HealthCare announces intent to acquire icometrix to strengthen neurology portfolio with brain MRI assessment solutions
summary: CHICAGO, September 10, 2025--GE HealthCare (Nasdaq: GEHC) today announced it has entered into an agreement to acquire icometrix, a company focused on providing AI-powered brain imaging analysis for neurological disorders such as Alzheimer’s disease to meet the growing demand for MRI in personalized treatment planning.
